Sentencas: A novel porous heterostructured Nd0.8SrL2CoO4 & PLUSMN;������/Nd0.5Sr0.5CoO3-������ (NSC214/113) cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) is developed to significantly enhance oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) kinetics.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared to single-phase materials, the fabricated porous heterostructured NSC214/113 shows optimized electrochemical properties, including a better conductivity, 20 times faster surface oxygen exchange kinetics, and a comparatively lower area-specific resistance (0.065 LI cm2 at 800 & DEG;C).
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The single cell with Ni-YSZIYSZGDCINSC214m3 configuration exhibits a high peak power density of 1.10 W cm -2 at 800 & DEG;C, superior to other cells reported in literature with similar heterostructured cathodes.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, the underlying mechanism of the ORR performance enhancement is further investigated, revealing that the formation of heterojunction can lead to a narrowed energy bandgap and a decrease of Co oxidation state, which further induce better conductivity, more available electrons and oxygen vacancies to enhance the ORR process.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Taken together, our research also provides new insights into potential application of artificial intelligence (AI) method involved in materials intelligent identification, cell state estimation, system diagnostic and optimization.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The revolutionary force of AI, especially in the field of new electrode material development is now advancing in its full swing.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: More and greater breakthroughs are still expected.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction kinetics by a porous heterostructured cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
